Example :

apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: srv01
  namespace: nisha
spec:
  type: NodePort or ClusterIP or LoadBalancer
  selector:
    type: php
  ports:
    - port: 80
      targetPort: 3000

Some Commands:
kubectl expose pod <pod-name> --port=<port> --target-port=<targetPort> --name=<service-name>               ‚ûù Create a Service for a Pod
kubectl expose deployment <deployment-name> --type=NodePort --port=<port>                                  ‚ûù Create a NodePort Service for a Deployment
kubectl create -f service.yaml                                                                             ‚ûù Create Service from YAML file
kubectl apply -f service.yaml                                                                              ‚ûù Create or update Service from YAML file
kubectl get services                                                                                       ‚ûù List all Services in current namespace
kubectl get svc -n <namespace>                                                                             ‚ûù List all Services in a specific namespace
kubectl describe service <service-name>                                                                    ‚ûù Show detailed info about a Service
kubectl delete service <service-name>                                                                      ‚ûù Delete a Service by name
kubectl edit service <service-name>                                                                        ‚ûù Edit Service configuration in-place


üîπ Service Access Commands

minikube service <service-name>                                             ‚ûù Open Service in browser (only with minikube)
minikube service <service-name> --url                                       ‚ûù Get URL for Service (only with minikube)
kubectl port-forward svc/<service-name> <local-port>:<service-port>         ‚ûù Forward local port to Service port
kubectl get endpoints <service-name>                                        ‚ûù Show Pod IPs linked to the Service
